</b></p>
<p>42. The Working Group has been invited to visit Argentina (follow-up visit), 
</p>
<p>Azerbaijan, Burkina Faso, India, Japan, Libya, Malta (follow-up visit), Nauru, Spain and 
</p>
<p>the United States of America, as well as the State of Palestine.  
</p>
<p>43. As indicated in paragraph 5 above, on 24 March 2014 the Government of Nauru 
</p>
<p>cancelled the scheduled visit of the Working Group, and has yet not accepted the new 
</p>
<p>proposed dates for the visit.  
</p>
